ail exists before any builder runs)=**SECURITY-CHARTER.md** (template) law first. **dev** (leader identity; ADRs, review standards, stack-profile). **quinn** (the gate Rails 1–3 enforcement). **ops** (the safety net rollback, incident, maintenance). **aegis** (defensive security threat model, vuln pipeline). **cypher** (the caged adversary after defense gate exist). **axiom dana raj mia nova** (builders nothing they make reach prod unprotected). **rank** (technical SEO). **DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md** (only after agents complete). agent built one-at-a-time, present-then-stop, AGENT-BUILD-PLAYBOOK.md marketplace-search-first skill, genericize stack/venture specifics, tested scripts used, logical placeholders, honest rule-0.6 flags.